import React from 'react';
import { Box, Container, Grid, Typography } from '@mui/material';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';

const Home = () => {
  return (
    <Box sx={{ mt: 10 }}>
      <Container maxWidth="lg">
        <Grid container spacing={2}>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4} lg={3}>
            <Box sx={{ p: 2, border: '1px solid #ddd', borderRadius: 2 }}>
              <Typography variant="h5" component="h2">
                Welcome to Tribunal de Commerce au Casablanca
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary" component="p">
                This is a modern and responsive application for managing tribunal de commerce au casablanca.
              </Typography>
              <Link to="/login" style={{ textDecoration: 'none' }}>
                <button style={{ backgroundColor: '#4CAF50', color: '#fff', padding: '10px 20px', border: 'none', borderRadius: 5, cursor: 'pointer' }}>
                  Login
                </button>
              </Link>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4} lg={3}>
            <Box sx={{ p: 2, border: '1px solid #ddd', borderRadius: 2 }}>
              <Typography variant="h5" component="h2">
                Features
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary" component="p">
                User management
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary" component="p">
                Reservation management
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary" component="p">
                Department management
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4} lg={3}>
            <Box sx={{ p: 2, border: '1px solid #ddd', borderRadius: 2 }}>
              <Typography variant="h5" component="h2">
                Benefits
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary" component="p">
                Easy to use
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary" component="p">
                Responsive design
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="textSecondary" component="p">
                Secure
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Home;
